      - ❌ FORBIDDEN: Rename any existing method
      - ❌ FORBIDDEN: Move or refactor existing logic
      - ❌ FORBIDDEN: Add new methods that introduce a parallel pattern

    Diff MUST be additive only. Code review will reject any structural change.

    🚨 CRITICAL — NFR-07 anti-parallelism guard: This task runs in COMPLETE ISOLATION. NO other
    repair task may be in flight while this task is executing. The TASK-INDEX.md wave structure
    enforces this — task 018 sits in its own dedicated Wave 1-C-isolated.

    Per CLAUDE.md NFR-01: NO production code changes; this is test infrastructure ONLY.
